(0)/ 364 (1)/ (n/a)
Patients, family members & visitors: 1369/ 1018 (2)/ (n/a)
Total: 1755 (0)/ 1382 (2)/ 294 (1)
Total no. patients in hospital: 79 (-3)
Recovering patients in convalescence: 26
Cases under treatment: 53 (-1) (including 16 patients in Intensive Care Unit)
Suspected cases: 1
